{"bangumi":{"date":"2020-01-09","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/1b/0e/270274_5me2F.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/1b/0e/270274_5me2F.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/1b/0e/270274_5me2F.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/1b/0e/270274_5me2F.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/1b/0e/270274_5me2F.jpg"},"summary":"水无月嘉祥的老家经营着一间历史悠久的日式点心老店。他决心以糕点师的身份，离开老家开一间自己的蛋糕店「La Soleil」。\r\n嘉祥发现从老家寄来的搬家行李中，竟然混进了两只在老家饲养的人型猫娘：巧克力和香草。嘉祥本来想将她们送回老家，但在两只猫娘的苦苦哀求下他也只好让步，开始和她们一起经营「La Soleil」。\r\n妹妹时雨，还有巧克力和香草的猫娘姐姐们：红豆、枫、桂、椰子，住在老家的猫娘们也都来店里帮忙，大家每天都过着开心热闹的生活。\r\n某天，巧克力在买东西的途中遇见一只陌生的小猫…。\r\n故事就从与这只令人在意的小猫的邂逅开始。温暖人心的猫娘故事即将上演！","name":"ネコぱら","name_cn":"NEKOPARA","tags":[{"name":"游戏改","count":324,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2020年1月","count":287,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL改","count":257,"total_cont":0},{"name":"后宫","count":210,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫娘","count":196,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":193,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":191,"total_cont":0},{"name":"艹猫","count":148,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌","count":130,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2020","count":120,"total_cont":0},{"name":"废萌","count":113,"total_cont":0},{"name":"FelixFilm","count":108,"total_cont":0},{"name":"百合","count":100,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Nekopara","count":58,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":57,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"轻百合","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山本靖貴","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萌系","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝莉","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山本靖贵","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2020年","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"拟人","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改编","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ネコぱら","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"佐伯伊織","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"已下载","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"八木侑紀","count":3,"total_cont":0}],"inf